{
  "page": "Orange emperors",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>The <b>orange emperors</b> are a newly founded dynasty of the <a href=\"/index.php/Golden_Empire_of_Yi_Ti\" title=\"Golden Empire of Yi Ti\">Golden Empire of Yi Ti</a>. Though the empire is officially ruled by <a href=\"/index.php/Bu_Gai\" title=\"Bu Gai\">Bu Gai</a>, seventeenth of the <a href=\"/index.php/Azure_emperors\" title=\"Azure emperors\">azure emperors</a>, general <a href=\"/index.php/Pol_Qo\" title=\"Pol Qo\">Pol Qo</a> has given himself imperial honors and named himself first of the orange emperors.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_yi_ti.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_yi_ti.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Known_orange_emperors\">Known orange emperors</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Orange_emperors&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Known orange emperors\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/God-Emperor\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"God-Emperor\">Emperor</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Pol_Qo\" title=\"Pol Qo\">Pol Qo</a>, Hammer of the <a href=\"/index.php/Jogos_Nhai\" title=\"Jogos Nhai\">Jogos Nhai</a>, first orange emperor</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References_and_notes\">References and notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Orange_emperors&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References and notes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf_yi_ti.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_yi_ti.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, Yi Ti.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403211152\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.008 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.009 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 100/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8538/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 298/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 48/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 526/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    5.126      1 -total\n 75.01%    3.845      1 Template:Ref\n 48.60%    2.491      1 Template:Ref/core\n 23.51%    1.205      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:19673-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403211152 and revision id 199263\n -->\n",
